    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the legendary S54B32 inline-six. This example features a recently overhauled VANOS system and a reinforced rear subframe, addressing critical chassis and valvetrain longevity. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission shifts with precision, directing power through a limited-slip differential. Suspension remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings, maintaining optimal camber under lateral load. With its individual throttle bodies providing instantaneous throttle response, this M3 delivers a visceral, high-RPM driving experience. A well-maintained driver's car with excellent mechanical integrity.",
